Dialogue: 600,0:00:03.00,0:00:05.00,Hint,,0,0,0,,标题源自Less Than Jake的歌曲"Last One Out of Liberty City"
Dialogue: 100,0:00:06.51,0:00:08.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}紫晶\N{\rENG}Amethyst.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:08.58,0:00:10.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你能别蹦达了吗?\N{\rENG}Do you mind not bouncing so much?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:11.92,0:00:13.15,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦\N{\rENG}Ooh.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:13.15,0:00:14.25,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}对不起\N{\rENG} Sorry.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:14.25,0:00:15.75,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我只是太兴奋了\N{\rENG}I'm just super excited.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:15.75,0:00:18.25,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}葛瑞格要带我去看演出!\N{\rENG}Greg is taking me to a show!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:18.26,0:00:19.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}演出?\N{\rENG}A show?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:19.56,0:00:23.56,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你指在剧～院那种?\N{\rENG}You mean like, at the thee-ay-terr?
Dialogue: 100,0:00:23.56,0:00:27.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不,是摇～滚演出!\N{\rENG}No. Like at a Rrrra-ha-hock show!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:27.77,0:00:29.33,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘿!要有乐队!在别人家里!\N{\rENG}Heh. Like a band! At a house!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:29.33,0:00:31.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}还有一大群人\N{\rENG}With a whole bunch of people hanging out
Dialogue: 100,0:00:31.60,0:00:33.10,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}一起嗨!\N{\rENG}and doing stuff!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:33.10,0:00:35.54,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}噢!天,这听起来酷毙了\N{\rENG}Ooh! Man, that sounds cool.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:35.54,0:00:37.27,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们晚上也有超棒的计划\N{\rENG}We have an awesome night planned, too.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:37.28,0:00:38.87,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们在拼拼图\N{\rENG}We're doing a puzzle.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:38.88,0:00:40.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哇哦\N{\rENG}Wow-wee.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:40.58,0:00:44.71,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我知道这听起来很逊,但可是612块的\N{\rENG}I know it sounds tame, but it has 612 pieces.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:44.72,0:00:46.42,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}并且没有四角!\N{\rENG}And no corners!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:46.42,0:00:48.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我发现一块边角\N{\rENG}I found a corner.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:50.69,0:00:52.59,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘿!\N{\rENG} Hey, y'all.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:52.59,0:00:54.69,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}葛瑞格,葛瑞格,葛瑞格,葛瑞格!\N{\rENG}Greg, Greg, Greg, Greg!
Dialogue: 100,0:00:54.69,0:00:57.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}看来你已经准备好在舞池里嗨了?\N{\rENG}So, you ready to throw down in the pit?
Dialogue: 600,0:00:54.69,0:00:57.46,Hint,,0,0,0,,这里的"pit"应该指的是"mosh pit"(狂舞区)--激烈,疯狂的舞蹈伴随硬核朋克配乐
Dialogue: 100,0:00:57.46,0:00:59.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我今天晚上去不了了.\N{\rENG}No pits for me tonight.
Dialogue: 100,0:00:59.30,0:01:00.73,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我对不起,紫晶.\N{\rENG}I'm sorry, Amethyst.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:00.73,0:01:02.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我完全忘了\N{\rENG}It totally slipped my mind
Dialogue: 100,0:01:02.20,0:01:04.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}巴尔布邀请我和维达利亚一起打牌\N{\rENG}that Barb invited me and Vidalia over for cards.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:04.30,0:01:06.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}扑克牌?\N{\rENG}Cards?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:06.14,0:01:08.74,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}谁带你们逃出养老院的?\N{\rENG}Who broke you guys out of the retirement home?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:08.74,0:01:11.04,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}相信我,我很想去演出的!\N{\rENG}Trust me, I'd love to go to the show!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:11.04,0:01:13.81,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但是巴尔布用我的邮件要挟我\N{\rENG}But barb threatened to hold my mail if I didn't.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:13.81,0:01:16.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}而且她不是一个空穴来风的女人\N{\rENG}And she's not a woman of empty threats.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:16.58,0:01:18.55,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好吧,算了\N{\rENG} Man, forget it.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:18.55,0:01:20.15,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我去不了演出了\N{\rENG}I can't go "show-lo."
Dialogue: 100,0:01:20.15,0:01:21.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}真是无聊\N{\rENG}That'll be boring.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:21.22,0:01:24.29,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你今晚可以和我们一起啊\N{\rENG}You could hang out with us tonight.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:24.29,0:01:25.99,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}一起拼拼图?呵呵\N{\rENG}And do a puzzle? Ha!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:25.99,0:01:28.49,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}也许我们也可以挤点时间织东西\N{\rENG}Maybe we can fit in some knitting, too.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:28.49,0:01:30.59,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我不是指这个\N{\rENG}That's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:30.59,0:01:34.33,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们可以和你一起去演出\N{\rENG}We could go to the show with you.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:34.33,0:01:35.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}真的?你确定?\N{\rENG}Really? Whaaaa?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:35.90,0:01:38.13,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你想去演出?\N{\rENG}You want to go to a show?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:38.14,0:01:41.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘈杂的音乐,推搡的人群?\N{\rENG}With loud music, and people pushing each other?
Dialogue: 100,0:01:41.31,0:01:44.67,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我已经完成了公平的互相伤害了\N{\rENG}I've done my fair share of pushing.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:44.68,0:01:46.51,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}喔～我觉得胳膊断了\N{\rENG}Ohh, I think it's broken.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:46.51,0:01:49.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你们俩从没见过我的另一面!\N{\rENG}You two just never saw me in action!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:49.48,0:01:53.08,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}打破每条规矩,反抗权威\N{\rENG}Breaking every rule, taking on the authorities,
Dialogue: 100,0:01:53.08,0:01:56.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我就能完全拥抱快乐的地球生活了!\N{\rENG}so I could indulge in the joys of life on Earth!
Dialogue: 100,0:01:56.82,0:01:58.62,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}噢!一片天空\N{\rENG}Oh! A sky piece.
Dialogue: 100,0:01:58.62,0:02:00.09,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好\N{\rENG}Nice.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:00.09,0:02:03.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}当然,你们要去的话可以开我的车\N{\rENG}Well, if you'd like to go, you guys can take the Dondai.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:03.66,0:02:05.03,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}谢谢你,葛瑞格\N{\rENG}Thank you, Greg.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:05.03,0:02:06.86,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}唔呼!演出!\N{\rENG}Whoo-hoo-hoo! Rock show!
Dialogue: 100,0:02:06.86,0:02:08.03,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}等等,珍珠\N{\rENG}Hold on, pearl.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:08.03,0:02:11.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这是个人类活动,不是宝石战争\N{\rENG}This is a human thing, not a Gem war.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:11.00,0:02:14.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}在你嗨翻前,你得先融入其中\N{\rENG}Before you rock out, you're gonna want to blend in.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:14.31,0:02:17.21,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}现在你看起来挺拽的了\N{\rENG}Now you're looking good.
Dialogue: 600,0:02:14.31,0:02:15.42,Hint,,0,0,0,,夹克背部的图案源自涅槃乐队"Nirvana"
Dialogue: 100,0:02:17.21,0:02:18.61,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦,是的\N{\rENG}Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:18.61,0:02:21.21,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但我可以变得更拽\N{\rENG}But I can make it look even gooder.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:21.21,0:02:25.15,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这很潮,因为领子本来不该这么立着\N{\rENG}It's cool, because the collar isn't supposed to go that way.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:25.15,0:02:27.05,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}厉害了我的破\N{\rENG}You a natural.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:27.05,0:02:29.45,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们快采购玩路上的零食了\N{\rENG}We're almost set on snacks for the road.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:29.45,0:02:31.69,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}就差饮料了\N{\rENG}We just need some beverages.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:31.69,0:02:33.89,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}草莓糖嗨\N{\rENG}Strawberry sugar shock shut down
Dialogue: 600,0:02:31.69,0:02:33.89,Hint,,0,0,0,,"草莓糖嗨"的Logo与Monster Energy相似
Dialogue: 100,0:02:33.89,0:02:37.19,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}或者老派苹果汁?\N{\rENG}or good old fashioned apple juice?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:37.19,0:02:39.53,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}绝对草莓糖嗨\N{\rENG}Definitely sugar shock shut down.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:39.53,0:02:41.83,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}它可以感染任何东西\N{\rENG}It turns everything red.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:43.57,0:02:45.47,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我也来一瓶,史蒂文\N{\rENG}I'll have one too, Steven.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:45.47,0:02:47.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我觉得今晚我可以试着喝点东西\N{\rENG}I think I'll try drinking tonight.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:47.71,0:02:49.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哇 真的?\N{\rENG}Wow, really?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:49.21,0:02:51.31,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我不知道你喜欢苹果汁啊?\N{\rENG}I didn't know you liked apple juice?
Dialogue: 100,0:02:51.31,0:02:54.24,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我有很多东西你不知道\N{\rENG}There's a lot you don't know about me, Steven.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:55.51,0:02:58.25,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那么,紫晶,介绍下我们要见的乐队\N{\rENG}So, Amethyst, tell me more about this band we're seeing.
Dialogue: 100,0:02:58.25,0:03:00.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们要去见麦克▪克罗\N{\rENG}We're going to see Mike Krol.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:00.99,0:03:03.09,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}他懂得真正的车库摇滚氛围\N{\rENG}He's got that real garage vibe.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:03.09,0:03:05.85,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那些怀念市郊的音乐\N{\rENG}Songs about being nostalgic for the suburbs.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:05.86,0:03:08.66,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}怀念市郊?切\N{\rENG}Nostalgic for the suburbs? Pssh.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:08.66,0:03:10.89,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}它们才存在了大概,70年?\N{\rENG}They've only existed for what? 70 years.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:10.90,0:03:14.00,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好吧,那么,当我们到达现场时\N{\rENG} Okay, so, when we get to the show,
Dialogue: 100,0:03:14.00,0:03:15.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}得显得这是你的场子\N{\rENG}you got to walk in like you own the place.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:24.01,0:03:28.34,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦!嘿,看那个!装B楷模\N{\rENG}Oh! Hey, right there. Perfect example.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:28.35,0:03:31.38,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}珍珠,你还好吗?\N{\rENG}Pearl, you okay?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:31.38,0:03:33.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃...\N{\rENG}Uh...
Dialogue: 100,0:03:33.02,0:03:37.39,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我没想到人类也可以有粉发\N{\rENG}I just didn't realize humans could come with pink hair.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:37.39,0:03:38.95,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}他们不是真有\N{\rENG} They don't.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:38.96,0:03:41.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你要去商店买一种液体\N{\rENG}You got to go to the store and get this goo.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:41.46,0:03:42.76,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}闻起来很特效\N{\rENG}It smells really bad,
Dialogue: 100,0:03:42.76,0:03:44.89,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}duang的一下头发就有你想要的颜色了\N{\rENG}and it turns your hair whatever color you want.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:44.90,0:03:46.03,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}为什么她这么做?\N{\rENG}Why would she do that?
Dialogue: 100,0:03:46.03,0:03:47.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你没什么不去问问?\N{\rENG}Why don't you go and ask her.
Dialogue: 100,0:03:47.30,0:03:48.63,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}也是!\N{\rENG}Hey, yeah!
Dialogue: 100,0:03:48.63,0:03:51.53,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们要和许多潮人交往\N{\rENG}We're about to go hang out with a bunch of cool humans.
