Dialogue: 100,0:04:33.94,0:04:35.33,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好吧,没人要说?\N{\rENG}Okay, nobody's gonna say it?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:35.60,0:04:37.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她看起来像妈妈\N{\rENG}She kind of looked like mom.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:37.18,0:04:39.35,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你看出来了.我看出来了.谁都看出来了.\N{\rENG}You noticed. I noticed. We all noticed.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:41.52,0:04:44.85,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}难怪你表现得像个呆瓜!\N{\rENG}That's why you were acting like such a goon!
Dialogue: 100,0:04:44.86,0:04:46.29,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不,才不是\N{\rENG}No, no. That's not it.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:46.29,0:04:48.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我与过去没有任何关联了\N{\rENG}I'm done thinking about the past.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:48.36,0:04:50.53,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}今晚,我只在乎将来\N{\rENG}Tonight, I'm all about the future.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:50.53,0:04:51.93,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我在前往一个演出\N{\rENG}I'm going to a show.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:51.93,0:04:55.03,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我是一个热爱人际关系的新宝石\N{\rENG}I'm a new Gem who loves socializing with humans.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:55.03,0:04:56.37,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}只是这样?\N{\rENG}That's what that was?
Dialogue: 100,0:04:56.37,0:04:59.20,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}算了,你又不在现场\N{\rENG}Look, you weren't there by the cups.
Dialogue: 100,0:04:59.20,0:05:02.30,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我本可以开口,这都是时辰的错\N{\rENG}I could've talked to her. The timing was just wrong.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:05.38,0:05:08.58,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}是那个女孩!她就在旁边!\N{\rENG}It's the girl! She's driving right next to us!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:11.55,0:05:12.95,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不可能!\N{\rENG}No way!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:12.95,0:05:14.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}人生第二春啊!\N{\rENG}You've got another chance!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:14.69,0:05:16.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}对!做点什么啊!\N{\rENG}Yeah! Do something!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:16.12,0:05:19.39,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}做什么?闪灯?按喇叭?\N{\rENG}Like what? Flash my lights? Honk at her?
Dialogue: 100,0:05:19.39,0:05:21.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}就给她来个酷炫的转身\N{\rENG}Just shoot her a look.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:21.23,0:05:22.22,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}等等\N{\rENG}Wait not yet.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:22.23,0:05:25.83,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好吧...现在!\N{\rENG}Okay, okay. You can look...now!
