Dialogue: 100,0:05:35.57,0:05:37.37,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}噢,她走了\N{\rENG}Ooh, and there she goes.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:37.37,0:05:41.18,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘿,也许她和我们去的一个地方\N{\rENG}Hey, maybe she's going to the same show as us.
Dialogue: 100,0:05:41.18,0:05:43.08,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我不确定,向那么酷的女孩\N{\rENG}I don't know, a girl that cool
Dialogue: 100,0:05:43.08,0:05:46.08,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}绝对知道十亿个今天晚上举行的演出\N{\rENG}probably knows about a billion shows going on tonight.
