Dialogue: 200,0:05:53.11,0:05:57.24,Background Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS_LYC}你只有15分钟陪伴我或者朋友\N{\rENG_LYC}And you had fifteen minutes to spend with me or your friends
