Dialogue: 200,0:06:01.35,0:06:05.51,Background Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS_LYC}或者去坐末班机到西海岸?\N{\rENG_LYC}Or would you take the last plane over the West Coast
Dialogue: 200,0:06:05.84,0:06:10.24,Background Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS_LYC}像这样的时刻,变卦的内心\N{\rENG_LYC}See at times like these with a change of heart
Dialogue: 200,0:06:10.24,0:06:14.24,Background Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS_LYC}一切已完结,来不及开始\N{\rENG_LYC}It was over and done before we had a start
Dialogue: 200,0:06:14.24,0:06:18.33,Background Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS_LYC}这挥之不去,我无所适从\N{\rENG_LYC}It goes on in my head and I'll wind up dead
Dialogue: 200,0:06:18.33,0:06:22.24,Background Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS_LYC}唱着,Sha-la-la-la-la-la-la-la-la\N{\rENG_LYC}Singing sha-la-la-la-la-la-la-la-la
Dialogue: 200,0:06:30.02,0:06:33.95,Background Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS_LYC}如果天上繁星坠向这大地\N{\rENG_LYC}What if all the stars came crashing to the ground
Dialogue: 200,0:06:33.95,0:06:37.84,Background Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS_LYC}而爆炸与火光在周围肆意蔓延\N{\rENG_LYC}And explosions and fires started happening all around
Dialogue: 200,0:06:38.29,0:06:43.11,Background Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS_LYC}你愿相信我并回家还是隔岸观火?\N{\rENG_LYC}Would you believe me and come home or sit back, let it be?
Dialogue: 200,0:06:43.11,0:06:45.95,Background Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS_LYC}我不能自己一人\N{\rENG_LYC}I can't do this by myself
