Dialogue: 200,0:07:02.71,0:07:06.64,Background Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS_LYC}如果我告诉你世界即将毁灭\N{\rENG_LYC}What if I told you that the world was gonna end
Dialogue: 200,0:07:06.64,0:07:10.46,Background Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS_LYC}你只有15分钟陪伴我或者朋友\N{\rENG_LYC}And you had fifteen minutes to spend with me or your friends
Dialogue: 200,0:07:10.69,0:07:14.86,Background Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS_LYC}我想我们都用不上手机\N{\rENG_LYC}I guess we don't even need to use the phone
Dialogue: 200,0:07:14.86,0:07:19.44,Background Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS_LYC}我不需你回应独自就很好\N{\rENG_LYC}I don't need your answer, I'll be spending it alone
Dialogue: 100,0:05:50.72,0:05:51.85,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}珍珠!\N{\rENG}Pearl!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:51.86,0:05:53.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}啊!\N{\rENG}Aaaah!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:54.73,0:05:56.09,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}\N{\rENG}Yeah, P!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:56.09,0:05:58.39,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你在干嘛?这是红灯!\N{\rENG}What are you doing? The light was red!
Dialogue: 100,0:05:58.40,0:06:00.33,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我知道\N{\rENG}I know.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:04.77,0:06:06.37,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她在那\N{\rENG}There she is.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:06.37,0:06:07.70,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你有什么计划?\N{\rENG}What's your plan?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:07.71,0:06:10.07,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}新珍珠,不计划\N{\rENG}New Pearl. No plan.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:10.07,0:06:11.77,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃,真的\N{\rENG}Ah, no kidding.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:12.88,0:06:15.64,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦\N{\rENG}Ooh.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:16.61,0:06:18.28,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}警察来了!\N{\rENG}The police want us!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:18.28,0:06:19.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦天\N{\rENG}Oh, snap!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:19.72,0:06:21.12,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我都干什么了?!\N{\rENG} What do I do?!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:21.12,0:06:22.72,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你要停在路边\N{\rENG}You have to pull over to the side
Dialogue: 100,0:06:22.72,0:06:24.29,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}然后出示你的证件\N{\rENG}and show them your license.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:24.29,0:06:26.59,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我没有证件\N{\rENG}I don't have a license.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:26.59,0:06:28.26,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦,好吧\N{\rENG} Oh, right.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:28.26,0:06:29.96,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但--但你年纪大啊!\N{\rENG}But -- But, you're old!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:29.96,0:06:31.79,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我该告诉车管所什么?\N{\rENG}What was I supposed to tell the DMV?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:31.80,0:06:33.36,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}难道我是外星人?\N{\rENG}That I'm from another planet?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:33.36,0:06:35.80,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我都不是公民,史蒂文!\N{\rENG}I'm not exactly a citizen, Steven!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:35.80,0:06:37.97,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那么我们该怎么做?\N{\rENG}Then what do we do?
Dialogue: 100,0:06:49.41,0:06:50.98,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}珍珠,你不能直接肇事逃脱!\N{\rENG}Pearl, you can't just drive away!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:50.98,0:06:52.41,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这可是很严肃的\N{\rENG}This is serious!
Dialogue: 100,0:06:52.42,0:06:54.65,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}珍珠,你真是个--\N{\rENG}Pearl, you're a total bad --
Dialogue: 100,0:06:54.65,0:06:57.69,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这就是为什么要系安全带\N{\rENG} This is why we buckle up.
Dialogue: 100,0:06:59.72,0:07:01.39,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}等等!\N{\rENG}Hold on!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:08.90,0:07:11.63,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}天呐撸\N{\rENG}Oh, boy.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:17.64,0:07:18.81,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘘\N{\rENG}Shh.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:21.15,0:07:22.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}他们走了吗?\N{\rENG}Are they gone?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:22.68,0:07:23.68,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我觉得是\N{\rENG}I think so.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:27.25,0:07:28.48,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}干!\N{\rENG}Guh!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:28.49,0:07:29.45,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}怎么了?\N{\rENG}What is it?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:29.45,0:07:31.69,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们没油了\N{\rENG} We're out of gas.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:31.69,0:07:33.09,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}噢,怎么会?\N{\rENG}Aw, what?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:33.09,0:07:35.02,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}等等!我去找个加油站\N{\rENG}Wait! I'll find a gas station.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:35.03,0:07:37.53,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}看起来最近的...\N{\rENG}Looks like the closest one is...
Dialogue: 100,0:07:37.53,0:07:39.46,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}20英里外\N{\rENG}20 miles away.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:44.70,0:07:46.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我简直没法相信\N{\rENG}I can't believe this.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:47.67,0:07:49.60,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}就差那么点\N{\rENG}I was so ready!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:49.61,0:07:51.87,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我非常想见你说的Krol\N{\rENG}I really wanted to see your Krol.
Dialogue: 100,0:07:51.88,0:07:54.71,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你是指?\N{\rENG}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 100,0:07:54.71,0:07:56.55,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我本要喝果汁\N{\rENG}I was going to drink a juice
Dialogue: 100,0:07:56.55,0:07:59.82,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}和穿这种裤子!\N{\rENG}and wear these  pants!
Dialogue: 100,0:07:59.82,0:08:01.15,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}咦～\N{\rENG}Ugh!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:01.15,0:08:04.49,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}然后--轻轻的推搡人群\N{\rENG}And --  -- hit people gently enough
Dialogue: 100,0:08:04.49,0:08:07.32,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}像你说的,不至于伤害他们那种\N{\rENG}as to not actually hurt them, and you'd say,
Dialogue: 100,0:08:07.32,0:08:10.16,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}"哇!珍珠真是酷!"\N{\rENG}"Wow! Pearl is really cool!"
Dialogue: 100,0:08:10.16,0:08:14.63,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但不,相反,我们放着喧嚣的音乐\N{\rENG}But no, instead, we drove to loud music,
Dialogue: 100,0:08:14.63,0:08:16.90,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}开着车在半夜追逐那神秘女子\N{\rENG}chased a mysterious woman into the night,
Dialogue: 100,0:08:16.90,0:08:18.50,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}还犯了法\N{\rENG}and broke the law.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:19.90,0:08:21.14,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我已经失去理智了\N{\rENG}I've lost my edge.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:21.14,0:08:24.07,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我本应呆在家里拼拼图的\N{\rENG}I should have stayed home with the puzzle.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:24.84,0:08:26.21,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}听听你自己\N{\rENG}Listen to yourself.
Dialogue: 100,0:08:26.21,0:08:28.84,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你真是顽固!\N{\rENG}You're so hard core!
Dialogue: 100,0:08:28.85,0:08:30.75,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}谁在乎裤子?\N{\rENG}Who cares about pants?
Dialogue: 100,0:08:30.75,0:08:32.65,Normal Dialog Text,,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你穿着它甩掉了警察!\N{\rENG}You gunned it from the cops!
